{"tid":647480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男大生猥褻堂妹　女友護航變補刀","createTime":"2018-04-30T00:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T18:38:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":93,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"f62d2580f10bc44b8808bdc6a52e2b186557b31c","tid":647480,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:54:22.000Z","msg":"「我沒摸過這麼大的胸部！」高雄一名男大生前年底至伯父家作客，竟趁機搓揉堂妹胸部，嚇得她驚慌失措，向父母告狀。男大生原坦承犯案，並簽下自白書，卻改口「被伯父一家所逼」。<br />\n<br />\n男大生的女友案發後主動傳訊息給堂妹，強調男大生很後悔，「我第一次看到他哭成這樣，這麼無助的感覺，我也好心疼」。法官憑此認定罪證確鑿，日前依對少年強制猥褻罪判10個月。<br />\n<br />\n判決書指出，這對堂兄妹從小感情非常好，長大後仍時常勾肩搭背、牽手出遊。前年底，男大生放假去堂妹家，兩人在房裡獨處，等堂妹結束與男友的視訊後，堂哥要求堂妹上床躺在身邊，被害少女不疑有他，不料堂哥突然撫摸她的大腿，還伸手到衣服內，撥開胸罩搓揉乳房。這時嬸嬸正好經過敲門，堂哥才縮手走出房間，被害人已嚇到不知如何是好。<br />\n<br />\n事發後被害少女找姊姊討論，兩姊妹決定告訴媽媽，沒想到媽媽聽完第一句話就斥責「怎麼一點也不會保護自己」，被害少女覺得無辜當場放聲大哭，因情緒激動換氣過度，引起父親注意，打電話給堂哥興師問罪。<br />\n<br />\n堂哥在電話裡賠不是，「開玩笑！開玩笑！我們玩過頭啦！」伯父要求男大生簽自白書，坦承未經堂妹同意做出「不軌行為」；男大生自首後翻供，反控遭伯父陷害。<br />\n<br />\n法官質疑，被害少女出現創傷後壓力症候群，屢次在宿舍痛哭、自責防備心不足，加上男大生黃姓女友的訊息，種種跡證證實男大生逾越親友分際，做出可能引起性慾之舉，痛責他不知悔改，依法判處10個月有期徒刑。本案可上訴。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180430/640_d3407898b6b46f0329b728c7d8db221d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180430%2F640_d3407898b6b46f0329b728c7d8db221d.jpg&h=fff01be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180430/1344112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180430%2F1344112&d=iasvbpCkUkVJl2lTLqQ2pNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ee58837b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180430%2F1344112&h=9f69b0c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180430/1344112</a>"},{"pid":"5da141a05f34e185ad85642e039e8e20220c68ae","tid":647480,"uid":11067,"like":142,"dislike":5,"score":137,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:57:23.000Z","msg":"種種跡證證實男大生逾越親友分際，做出可能引起性慾之舉<br />\n<br />\n成功引起咗性慾嘅話就乜事都冇啦，伯母阻人扑嘢罪大滔天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc7cfa927ef468d1f01014760e2d08e6b03d047","tid":647480,"uid":1060,"like":6,"dislike":76,"score":-70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:58:40.000Z","msg":"死啦 我覺得好正常姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86918d984321a6678260a32c750cbb8a21809780","tid":647480,"uid":139126,"like":65,"dislike":65,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:59:14.000Z","msg":"咁未揸過咁大波丫嘛 揸一下會死咩"},{"pid":"1c8bfb5d66e72642a8ef51ba15c626907da6e1c2","tid":647480,"uid":11962,"like":80,"dislike":3,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:00:02.000Z","msg":"台灣又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f76a2fbb4c7fdc4c0646d8abb28450014227ec","tid":647480,"uid":180124,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:03:04.000Z","msg":"個堂哥衰在少左一堆前戲"},{"pid":"e53e625a66933f37de3fc53241a6b29ca7f5f1e3","tid":647480,"uid":74361,"like":11,"dislike":319,"score":-308,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/next-photos/NextMag/1182/640pixfolder/E1182_030__MG_9219a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FNextMag%2F1182%2F640pixfolder%2FE1182_030__MG_9219a.jpg&h=b2e002d7&s={SIZE}\" />搵左張好少少，大家頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7a755780d82607dfa9670bf8fea18c4bbd4e7f","tid":647480,"uid":1993,"like":191,"dislike":7,"score":184,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/090628_748c5d5a90b740845ce4ae73919beb1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F090628_748c5d5a90b7408